Create a UserPreferencesCard component that allows users to configure their account settings. The layout should be as follows:

A Card acts as the container.

Inside the card:

A Text element titled "User Preferences" at the top

A Toggle switch to turn "Dark Mode" on or off

A Checkbox labeled "Enable 2FA"

A Select dropdown for selecting time zone. Available options: PST, EST, GMT

A Button labeled "Save Settings" at the bottom of the card

The dark mode setting is controlled by the variable "darkMode".
The 2FA setting is stored in the variable "twoFA".
The selected time zone is stored in the variable "timeZone".